value.title: East Bay Climate Changemakers
value.description:
About Event

​Calling all climate-conscious denizens of the Bay Area! Come and join the East Bay chapter of Climate Changemakers for the most productive Hour of your day! We’ll get up to speed on a timely climate policy issue, learn how we can move the needle this week, and then actually take action – all within the hour. 🌎

​Curious what to expect at the Hour of Action? Read more here.

​Agenda:
🍻 5:30-6pm: Build climate community - chat, catch up, grab a drink or a snack and settle in
🚀 6-7pm:
